.Dd April 19, 2016
.Dt FLYCATCHER 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm flycatcher
.Nd Detect and impede port scanners
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl i Ar interface
.Pp
.Nm
.Fl V
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
daemon attempts to detect port scanners and, if possible, slow them
down by forging responses to keep them occupied.
